Typing :help followed by the <Up> key brings up Ex commands that started 
with the word “help.”

Press / to bring up the search prompt, scroll backward and forward through 
previous searches with the <Up> and <Down> keys. 

q: -> command-line window: Ex mode history

:q -> close the command-line window 

Command 	Action
****************************** ******************************
q/ 		Open the command-line window with history of searches
q: 		Open the command-line window with history of Ex commands
ctrl-f 		Switch from Command-Line mode to the command-line window
